snippet.title: beatmania (Arcade / 1997) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
The original beatmania, emulated via MAME 0.182 (using the new PortAudio output module).

1:09 jam master '73 - jam jam reggae "REGGAE"
3:00 MIRAK - OVERDOSER (romo mix) "TECHNO"
4:45 DJ BATTLE
6:14 prophet~31 - 2 gorgeous 4U "BREAK~BTS"
8:05 e.o.s. - e~emotion "RAVE"
9:45 DJ nagureo - u gotta groove "HIP~HOP"
11:31 LOVEMINTS - LOVE SO GROOVY "SOUL"
13:26 DJ Nagureo - 20, novemver (single mix) "HOUSE"
15:25 Credits

I'll get around to capturing the doubles play songs soon.

https://remywiki.com/AC_bm_1st

(Lots of flashing lights in this game; it looks awesome, but be careful if you're sensitive to that!)
